      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
<div class = "row">
  <h1 class="about-homepage">As the situation in the Eastern parts of Ukraine is becoming a large-scale humanitarian crisis, Nataliya Foundation needs your support to maintain its 5 large-scale relief programmes across the country </h1>
  <br>
  <div class = "hold-points">
    <div class ="home-row"><h1 class ="home-number">1</h1> <h2 class="five-branch">
      Medico-social and material assistance to victims and families of the deceased during mass protests in Ukraine</h2></div>

    <div class ="home-row"><h1 class ="home-number">2</h1> <h2 class="five-branch">Medical treatment and long-duration rehabilitation to wounded during EuroMaidan and in Eastern oblasts</h2></div>

    <div class ="home-row"><h1 class ="home-number">3</h1> <h2 class="five-branch">Psychotherapeutic assistance to direct victims, familiy members and witnesses of mass protests in Ukraine</h2></div>

    <div class ="home-row"><h1 class ="home-number">4</h1> <h2 class="five-branch">Care for internally displaced persons from Crimea and Eastern oblasts of Ukraine</h2>
    </div>

    <div class ="home-row"><h1 class ="home-number">5</h1> <h2 class="five-branch">Assistance to victims of humanitarian crisis in Eastern Ukraine</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class = "divider"></div>

